//*             values". The length of new strAction is stored in wActionLen.                     *
//*                                                                                             *
//*			ACTION_DATA(parameter, [parameters]):                                               *
//*             This set of function append to string "strAction_Data" all function "parameters   *
//*             values". The length of new strAction_Data is stored in wAction_DataLen.           * 
//*			                                                                                    *
//*			COMMENT(parameter):                                                                 *
